@chatBase = http://localhost:8003/api/v1
@authToken = user_token_123

### Listar miembros activos del chat
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/members/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar miembros — filtrar por estado
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/members/?status=pending
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar todos los miembros (cualquier estado)
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/members/?status=all
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Invitar miembros al chat
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/members/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "member_ids": [10, 20, 30]
}


### Actualizar estado de un miembro (ej. pending → active)
PATCH {{chatBase}}/chats/1/members/10/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "status": "active"
}


### Eliminar un miembro del chat — responde 204
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/members/10/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Cambiar rol de un miembro
PATCH {{chatBase}}/chats/1/members/10/role/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "role": "editor"
}


### Abandonar el chat (self-serve) — responde 204
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/members/leave/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
